<body>
<p>Reports redundant <code>@PathVariable</code> name declaration when it matches a parameter name.
  The quick-fix removes the explicit name attribute from the annotation.</p>
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @GetMapping("/{orderId}")
  public Order getOrder(@PathVariable("orderId") Long orderId)
    return return orderRepository.findOne(orderId);
  }
</code></pre>
<p>After the quick-fix is applied the result looks like:</p>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @GetMapping("/{orderId}")
  public Order getOrder(@PathVariable Long orderId)
    return orderRepository.findOne(orderId);
  }
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>